Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	***** NickServ Help *****
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	NickServ allows users to 'register' a nickname, and stop
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	others from using that nick. NickServ allows the owner of a
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	nickname to disconnect a user from the network that is using
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	their nickname.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	If a registered nick is not used by the owner for 90
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	days, NickServ will drop the nickname, allowing it to be
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	re-registered.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	The following commands are available:
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  CERT            Changes and shows your nickname CertFP authentication list.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  GHOST           Reclaims use of a nickname.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  IDENTIFY        Identifies to services for a nickname.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  INFO            Displays information on registrations.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  LISTCHANS       Lists channels that you have access to.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  LISTGROUPS      Lists groups that you have access to.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  LOGOUT          Logs your services session out.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  REGAIN          Regain usage of a nickname.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  REGISTER        Registers a nickname.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  RELEASE         Releases a services enforcer.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  SENDPASS        Email registration passwords.
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	The following additional commands are available:
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	  ACC, HELP, SETPASS, STATUS, TAXONOMY, VERIFY
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	For more information on a NickServ command, type:
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	/msg NickServ HELP <command>
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	For a verbose listing of all NickServ commands, type:
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	/msg NickServ HELP COMMANDS
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	If you're having trouble, or you need some additional help,
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	you may wish to join the help channel #SpotChat
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	 
Dec 09 21:07:05 -NickServ-	***** End of Help *****
